room_title: Escape room "417 Lounge" by 417 Escape Artist in Springfield (MO)
room_description: The year is 1929. James Covington, a wealthy New York stockbroker, has been found pushing up daisies and it’s up to you and your team to figure out who the culprit is! Was it his promiscuous wife Evelyn? His shady business partner Mr. Eldridge? Crack the case of this roaring 20’s caper and become the next 417 Escape Artist!
